{"tid":401110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜蔡若蓮喪子後署任教育局長","createTime":"2017-09-15T11:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T11:13:35.000Z","uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1b9fd84bc794f3e735be6d84f575c43870f1b4","tid":401110,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄將於下星期一（9月18日）傍晚啟程前往北京訪問，周三（9月20日）回港。<span style=\"color: red;\">期間由副局長蔡若蓮署任教育局局長，顯示蔡若蓮經歷喪子之痛後現已回到工作崗位。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府新聞稿指，楊潤雄訪京期間將會與中國教育部官員舉行會議，及禮節性拜訪國務院港澳事務辦公室及北京市教育委員會。他亦會於北京出席活動，與一批正在內地升讀大學的香港學生會面，了解他們的日常生活情況及需要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E8%A8%AA%E4%BA%AC-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2580%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E4%25BA%25AC-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a6e2516f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2580%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E4%25BA%25AC-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&h=ece704e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E8%A8%AA%E4%BA%AC-%E